    <h3  class="f4-mktg color-fg-muted pb-2" aria-hidden="true"> The New York Times</h3>
    <p  class="h6-mktg color-fg-default py-1 pb-sm-4 text-semibold" aria-hidden="true">The New York Times uses GitHub to keep developers focused on code, not checklists.</p>
